title: Armin van Buuren - A State Of Trance Radio Top 30 - March / Apri
description:
Armin van Buuren - A State Of Trance Radio Top 30 - March / April / May 2014 (2014) 

          Trance, Uplifting Trance, Vocal Trance | Armada Music Bundles

              320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 204 | 01:56:44 | 271 Mb


Its time once again for the tip-top -- the very best of ASOT for the last 3 months. With 31 massive tunes coming from new talents and trance masters alike, theres an unreal amount of ability packed into this tracklist. Armin van Buuren, Andrew Rayel, GAIA, Aly & Fila, Markus Schulz, and a wide selection of Armada young guns contribute to the selection. Tune in, these are anthems that have been storming the world for the last 3 months.
